## A streamlined .gitignore for modern .NET projects
## including temporary files, build results, and
## files generated by popular .NET tools. If you are
## developing with Visual Studio, the VS .gitignore
## https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/VisualStudio.gitignore
## has more thorough IDE-specific entries.
##
## Get latest from https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Dotnet.gitignore

## 🛠 Generelle utviklingsfiler
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
*.log
*.pem
Thumbs.db

## 🔥 Git-debugging og cache
.gitignore
!.gitignore
.gitmodules
.gitattributes

## 📦 NPM & Yarn (felles for backend og frontend)
node_modules/
.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions
.npmrc
.npm/

## 🛠 .NET / ASP.NET Core (Backend i `AFBack/`)
AFBack/bin/
AFBack/obj/
AFBack/.env

## ⚡ Next.js (Frontend i `activitynext/`)
activitynext/node_modules/
activitynext/.next/
activitynext/out/
activitynext/.turbo/
activitynext/.swc/
activitynext/.vercel/
activitynext/build/

## 🔑 Miljøvariabler (felles for hele repoet)
.env*
.env.local
.env.development
.env.production
.env.test

## 🧪 Testing & Coverage
coverage/
*.coverage
TestResults/
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/

## 🏗 Bygg- og loggfiler
*.binlog
*.tsbuildinfo
*.lock
